{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 1653518, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Aliok", "body": "Ji Firepaw is the NPC that was at the center of a hot debate regarding the presence of sexism in dialogue and behavior in the game.\n\nOriginal text for male and female characters, respectively, for the quest [quest=29522].\n[quote]Hello, friend! You've got a strong look to you! I bet you're all the rage with the ladies! Join me! You and I are going to be good friends![/quote]\n[quote]Hello, friend! You're some kind of gorgeous, aren't you? I bet you can't keep the men off of you! Join me! You and I are going to be good friends![/quote]\n\nHis new text on the beta is thus:\n[quote]You seem poised and ready. I can tell we are going to be good friends.[/quote]\n\nI only make mention here of this because there are passionate feelings on both sides and I don't want what happened on the official WoW forum and WoW Insider to occur on Wowhead. Please, do not discuss it here. Thank you.", "date": "2012-04-13T20:23:36-05:00", "rating": 40, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "People thought that was offensive? I don't want to live on this planet anymore", "creationdate": "2012-10-06T20:10:56-05:00", "id": 580455, "rating": 24, "commentid": 1653518, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Yzzami", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Something out of nothing, absolutely nothing...", "creationdate": "2012-10-19T09:10:32-05:00", "id": 587565, "rating": -5, "commentid": 1653518, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Lightbrand", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Weak people with a weak mind get offended by almost everything. It's a sad world.", "creationdate": "2013-03-03T17:15:17-06:00", "id": 637198, "rating": 7, "commentid": 1653518, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Daren88", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Gee, sexism in a game where the same gear looks like skimpy lingerie on female characters and normal on male characters, without even giving you the choice not to have your female character look like a stripper? (And of course, if you complain then you're \"annoying\"?", "creationdate": "2013-08-24T06:16:48-05:00", "id": 686993, "rating": 5, "commentid": 1653518, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "cephadex", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "And they refer to this later on when Ji is watching Aysa meditate when he gives you the quest Rewritten Wisdoms. There's an optional dialogue prompt where your character says 'Maybe you should talk to her.' Ji responds, 'Should I tell her she's gorgeous, or would she find that creepy? Maybe I could tell her I admire her poise--but then she might think I don't have any personality!'", "creationdate": "2014-04-27T01:45:57-05:00", "id": 742767, "rating": 6, "commentid": 1653518, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "vansieg", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2012-04-13T21:51:34-05:00", 1, "Aliok"]}
