{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 1756258, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Jehosaphat", "body": "As a Pandarian warrior, Ji and I had many adventures together.\n\nTogether we awoke elemental spirits, mourned deaths of fallen friends, showed our compassion to strangers, healed a scar on our very homeland, I encouraged him to follow his heart for the woman he admired and loved but supported him as we took a separate path away from desires and stood side by side as we pledged our allegiance to Garrosh Hellscream and the Horde understanding full well that we might have to pick up arms against our former friends.\n\nYet, afterward, when I went back to speak and have tea with my old friend he stared at me blankly and said to me, \"I have nothing to teach you, warrior.\"\n\nIt was the 'warrior' that stung the most...", "date": "2012-11-03T13:12:12-05:00", "rating": 69, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "*gentle pat on the shoulder*", "creationdate": "2012-12-10T15:57:37-06:00", "id": 610233, "rating": 5, "commentid": 1756258, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "bossfight1", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Garrosh, btw. *Sniffles and cries.*", "creationdate": "2013-07-07T13:43:26-05:00", "id": 675642, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1756258, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Beytran70", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "whoa oops, fixed. Thanks!", "creationdate": "2014-08-16T23:45:52-05:00", "id": 765218, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1756258, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Jehosaphat", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "As a rogue pandaren, i stumbled upon him today. And to my surprise, his dialogue and text have changed! He was happy to see me again :')", "creationdate": "2016-07-23T21:43:35-05:00", "id": 953962, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1756258, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Myahomi", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2014-08-16T23:45:25-05:00", 1, "Jehosaphat"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 1760404, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Darkflash", "body": "Does anyone else find it weird he's still level 10 after you leave the Isle, but on the Alliance Aysa had a quick boost to level 90? I would think since they're masters and pretty much the leaders of the Pandaren on those factions, they would both be level 90, or at least boss level. Hopefully Blizz will see that, and level up more. Just makes him seem weak, just because he chose the Horde.", "date": "2012-11-10T15:33:21-06:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
