{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 1750751, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Sharkon", "body": "\"Maybe you should talk to her.\"\r\n\r\n[quote]Aysa? I don't know what to say to her. Should I tell her she's gorgeous, or would she find that creepy? Maybe I could tell her I admire her poise - but then she might think I don't have any personality![/quote]\r\n\r\nThis bonus dialogue is an in-joke referencing a minor controversy from the early Mists of Pandaria Beta. In [quest=29522], Ji Firepaw originally complimented female characters for their beauty in the quest's completion text. Some players complained that this was offensive and \"creepy,\" and the dialogue was changed so that he complimented the player's poise instead... which led to other players complaining that the change stripped away all his personality.", "date": "2012-10-26T08:25:18-05:00", "rating": 16, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 1772601, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "SharpDustySuits", "body": "This may be true for him all around Shen-zin Su, but in Morning Breeze Village, while turning in the quest 'Morning Breeze Village' he asks for a hug. If you /hug him, he warmly hugs you back.  :)", "date": "2012-11-30T22:24:30-06:00", "rating": 10, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
